snippet.title: Clid the Snail - Release Announcement | PS5, PS4
snippet.description: Watch the new trailer of Clid the Snail, a dark fable about a grumpy humanoid snail armed to the teeth. A Top-Down Shooter focused on narrative and a mindful combat system.
